@node "Translation" "Shameless plug..."

   I can translate commercial software's documentation or hardware 
   manuals, in fact anything technical, from English (or American)
   to French and vice versa. 
   
   I have a very good knowledge and experience of the Amiga and 
   computing in general.
   
   Please click @{" here " link "Adapter"} for contact address.
      
@endnode      

@node "history" "Guide history:"

   History:
   ~~~~~~~
   
   1.22 -  4-Oct-94 - Initial version released to Aminet.
   
   1.23 - 27-Jan-96 - Corrected version received from Jean-Michel Bezeau
                      regarding '/' which didn't appear because they were
                      not escaped by another '/'. Thanks Jean-Michel.

@endnode

